cture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Washborne was born in 1353, in Ashford, Devon, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Margaret Cotterell. He died in 1386, at the age of 33."},"et":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","1386":"1386","1396":"1396","1373":"1373","1350":"1350","Ashford, Devon, England":"Ashford, Devon, England"},"fi":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","1386":"1386","1396":"1396","1373":"1373","1350":"1350","Ashford, Devon, England":"Ashford, Devon, England"},"fr":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","1386":"1386","1396":"1396","1373":"1373","1350":"1350","Ashford, Devon, England":"Ashford, Devon, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"William Washborne est né en 1353, à Ashford, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Margaret Cotterell. Il est décédé en 1386, à l’âge de 33 ans."},"de":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","1386":"1386","1396":"1396","1373":"1373","1350":"1350","Ashford, Devon, England":"Ashford, Devon, England","lifeSummary":"William Washborne wurde 1353 in Ashford, Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Margaret Cotterell mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1386 im Alter von 33 Jahren."},"ht":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","1386":"1386","1396":"1396","1373":"1373","1350":"1350","Ashford, Devon, England":"Ashford, Devon, England"},"hu":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","1386":"1386","1396":"1396","1373":"1373","1350":"1350","Ashford, Devon, England":"Ashford, Devon, England"},"id":{"1353–1386":"1353–1386","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1373–1410":"1373–1410","1410":"1410","1353":"1353","138